attribution.en: Mr. Andrew Saxton (Parliamentary Secretary to the President of the Treasury Board and for Western Economic Diversification, CPC)

content.fr: Monsieur le Président, si les questions nos 1 322 à 1 325 pouvaient être transformées en ordre de dépôt de document, les documents seraient déposés immédiatement.
content.en: Mr. Speaker, if Questions Nos. 1,322 to 1,325 could be made orders for returns, these returns would be tabled immediately.

h2.en: Questions Passed as Orders for Returns
